message:
test(input-types): expand from 60 to 81 tests for keyboard/mouse input types (wa-2pgd9)

Add 21 new tests covering: ctrl_mapping() for alpha (lower/upper),
special chars, digits 2-8, and unmapped chars; Modifiers::remove_positional_mods();
to_string_with_separator with UnixLong and Emacs rendering;
KeyCode::normalize_shift() for lowercase/uppercase/non-alpha/no-shift;
KeyEvent::normalize_ctrl() for control chars and normal chars;
MousePress variant distinctness; MouseEventKind VertWheel/HorzWheel;
MouseButtons all variants (X1, X2); WindowDecorations default and
string roundtrip.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

